{"id":232120553,"title":"讓咖啡更好喝的濾水壺推薦~","content":"大家好\n剛入坑手沖咖啡不久\n買了一個還不錯的濾水壺推薦一下\nBWT是我爬文的時候發現有網友推\n因為有鎂離子濾芯，所以過濾後的水也會比較甜\n可以把咖啡的風味帶出來\n其實可以買鹽回來自己試\n不過我還沒那麼專業\n所以就入手BWT了\nhttps://i.imgur.com/TgEgaxK.jpg\n濾水壺有電子式濾芯更換顯示器，方便查看濾芯的使用狀況，還有要不要更換\n把手的部分我覺得蠻好握的，倒水也不會不順\n口感的話，水我覺得有變好喝\n然後我用ucc職人咖啡的濾掛包沖兩杯，一杯有過濾，一杯無過濾\n室友(木舌人)跟我都覺得過濾後比較好喝~\n個人感覺泡出來的咖啡酸味有減輕\n\n以上，小小心得\n給想買濾水壺的人參考","excerpt":"大家好，剛入坑手沖咖啡不久，買了一個還不錯的濾水壺推薦一下，BWT是我爬文的時候發現有網友推，因為有鎂離子濾芯，所以過濾後的水也會比較甜，可以把咖啡的風味帶出來，其實可以買鹽回來自己試，不過我還沒那麼","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"6120536f-6a70-49bb-8891-ec0ba2f4b396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-09-19T02:45:01.750Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-19T03:15:39.073Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":21,"tags":[],"topics":["濾水壺","bwt","鎂離子"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"咖啡","forumAlias":"coffee","school":"國立嘉義大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":20},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/TgEgaxK.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"547f9f11-be36-4424-ba61-0f0411289cd2","url":"https://i.imgur.com/TgEgaxKl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/TgEgaxKl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/TgEgaxKl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-19T02:45:01.750Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-19T03:15:39.073Z"},{"id":"547f9f11-be36-4424-ba61-0f0411289cd2","url":"https://i.imgur.com/TgEgaxK.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/TgEgaxK","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/TgEgaxKl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-19T02:45:01.750Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-19T03:15:39.073Z"}],"postAvatar":""}